{"tid":1533063,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"醒啦香港人！時移勢易出得黎行就預左比人扑爆你，太子站一事話你知唔好妄想和理非就安全！","createTime":"2019-09-02T16:06:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T06:09:51.000Z","uid":92479,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3422e2c72651fbc6817edd859e14006744b18336","tid":1533063,"uid":92479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:06:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">而家已經無法律，警權無限大，想點都得！</span><br />\n機場都唔再好似之前咁咁安全！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">跟返個時代走啦好唔好，糾正你落後既認知<br />\n唔係要大家怕左唔出黎，而係要有危機意識，香港人最缺乏呢樣野<br />\n唔係諗住食花生就無事，被捕被虐待係無意義既！<br />\n想勇武既就全力進攻，最忌打與走之間模稜兩可咁，但一定要係對等武力／高一級武力！<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n梁天琦：抗爭抱「對等武力」原則；但何謂「對等武力」？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1481490\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1481490</a><br />\n<br />\n點撚解次次入夜9點後都唔撚識走？唔撚係對等武力咪撚硬迫啦仆街！又有兄弟被捕喇！學紅隧咁做得唔得！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1400826\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1400826</a><br />\n<br />\n點解入黑警？<br />\n巴閉囉，英雄主義，疊馬。<br />\n我唔妥你，我可以𢭃你；<br />\n我唔鍾意你，我可以𢱕你。<br />\n𡃁仔你睥咩呀？出嚟隻揪吖！<br />\n隻揪呀！<br />\n揪我吖！揪吖！<br />\n我揪你你揪我，點呀？<br />\n你見過冧友未呀？你見過死人未呀？"},{"pid":"8c5adcdaca9d6c4358995c073304362b05d70086","tid":1533063,"uid":92479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:08:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.whatscap.com/a77/c2e/a77c2e79ece277b2837f85bccba9066d2e28ca17_n.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.whatscap.com%2Fa77%2Fc2e%2Fa77c2e79ece277b2837f85bccba9066d2e28ca17_n.png&h=4ed939ff&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0ca1a94d3f2aa1a5e2a688f686342e5b425cd702","tid":1533063,"uid":92479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:09:55.000Z","msg":"最忌好似牛佬呢啲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.whatscap.com/3c6/263/3c626370ed908e8dc1097ca2c10771c43577af01_n.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.whatscap.com%2F3c6%2F263%2F3c626370ed908e8dc1097ca2c10771c43577af01_n.png&h=d48d00a4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"64363be7611344c72aa37a0d7b3ad452cfb40f25","tid":1533063,"uid":10070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:10:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7235ea851b522e8971185f0a355517573be8250","tid":1533063,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:10:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a625c21985f9164bac1d2a2a0820636db3c59140","tid":1533063,"uid":92479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:11:16.000Z","msg":"最忌走住屌<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ZBFZr-AU3I0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZBFZr-AU3I0&d=7ie9SmB3qTQYrTFhvLfIgcorGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=3d05583a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ZBFZr-AU3I0</a>"},{"pid":"d2bfa48e3f240b75e275029eb3abbe3f02a19ae8","tid":1533063,"uid":92479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:12:19.000Z","msg":"我朋友因爲講左句 ：警察你跌左個良心 比人打到頭破血流 比人拉左<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1532848\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1532848</a>"},{"pid":"2f1cdd8562f7ce96e8008f69fa4329ed7a4f190c","tid":1533063,"uid":92479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:15:45.000Z","msg":"from事主 msg:<br />\n<br />\n我放工搭車到大圍<br />\n有個警察無啦啦推個師奶埋牆<br />\n我走去問乜事呀<br />\n3個男警推撞我好多次<br />\n我未婚夫 將我拉開，但警繼續推撞我同佢<br />\n最後佢拉左我男友話佢襲警<br />\n<br />\n我依家係田心警署入面<br />\n有律師入到秇<br />\nI m safe,xxxx is safe <br />\n佢用警署內線同我報平安<br />\n已叫佢乜都唔好講唔好簽，等律師搞<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10156695244678107&amp;id=631703106\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D10156695244678107%26id%3D631703106&d=7ie9SmB3qTQYrTFhvLfIgcorGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=05cf19da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10156695244678107&amp;id=631703106</a><br />\n[求片」大圍尋晚唔止師奶！仲有對情侣幫口就被人屈襲警！！！！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1531225\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1531225</a>"},{"pid":"bcc52649a8b1c7527fef1e89c49e70127ae01e14","tid":1533063,"uid":92479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:17:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/p0FVAEF1LZc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fp0FVAEF1LZc&d=7ie9SmB3qTQYrTFhvLfIgcorGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=349f08c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/p0FVAEF1LZc</a>"},{"pid":"319498fd0ab2d62520eb7088bb39d95ef571775f","tid":1533063,"uid":92479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:18:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190902/large/1567356374_4050.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190902%2Flarge%2F1567356374_4050.gif&h=08e63128&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b08cbc7a443d1110d146f1f5b91fe1ea1412467c","tid":1533063,"uid":92479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:18:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/4NfzHEZ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4NfzHEZ.gif&h=6b05e5f0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1c982391cf12c95f981c417614b31f130f1e72f2","tid":1533063,"uid":92479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:20:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/gz5dM6EbWnA\" data